<!-- About -->

<div class="section">
<h3>About This System</h3>
<p>
This platform helps users report missing persons, search cases, and use AI-based image matching
to identify missing individuals quickly and efficiently.
</p>
</div>

<!-- How to Report -->

<div class="section">
<h3>How to Report a Missing Person</h3>
<ul>
<li>Go to the Report Page</li>
<li>Fill in all details (name, age, location)</li>
<li>Upload a clear photo</li>
<li>Submit the form</li>
</ul>
</div>

<!-- How to Search -->

<div class="section">
<h3>How to Search a Missing Person</h3>
<ul>
<li>Go to Search Page</li>
<li>Enter name, age, or location</li>
<li>Upload image for AI search</li>
<li>Click search button</li>
</ul>
</div>

<!-- AI Feature -->

<div class="section">
<h3>AI Face Recognition</h3>
<p>
The system uses AI to compare uploaded images with the database of missing persons.
If a match is found, it helps identify the person quickly.
</p>
</div>

<!-- Safety Tips -->

<div class="section">
<h3>Safety Tips</h3>
<ul>
<li>Always provide correct information</li>
<li>Do not upload fake data</li>
<li>Contact police for emergency cases</li>
<li>Keep personal data secure</li>
</ul>
</div>

